{"type":null,"faqId":13071,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02  如何升级手机？","answer":"<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37716\" width=\"112\" height=\"59\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\"><span>为防止手机内存中的用户数据（如：联系人、信息、通话记录等）在升级时被删除，建议升级前备份手机数据。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在线升级：在线升级前，请连接移动网络或</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>手机升级</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统软件更新</span><span> &gt; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在线升级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37717\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本地升级：进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">下载软件升级包，插入</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡，并将升级包中的</span><span> dload </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件夹放入</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡根目录下。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">然后进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>手机升级</b></span> <span>&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统软件更新</span> </b><span>&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本地升级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据屏幕提示完成升级。您也可以参考下载的软件升级包中的升级指导。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37718\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":9,"unUseful":12,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4020","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1401961750000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":2791,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":4,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":4.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}